Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After Gon parts ways with Killua \Nin order to stop the selection, he finds himself under attack \Nby new Chimera Ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:15.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}知らんぷり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:15.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An owl and a bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:18.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうだ　あいつなら ゴンを気に入ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:18.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're both nocturnal creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:21.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何とかしてくれるかも ん？　あ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:21.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hunters of the night! From the left?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}アホ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:33.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何だ？ 顔見知りでもいたのか？ あ　いやぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:33.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The owl's feathers? Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:39.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ。 あの時の女！ 何だ　シズクの知り合いか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:39.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The bat's wings are so loud, \NI can't hear the owl at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう一度。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If the owl is acting in a support role, I should focus on the sound of the bat's wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:01.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}レディ…　ゴー！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:01.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right after the owl attacks, \Nthe bat will attack! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう一度。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn, I missed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}レディ…　ゴー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bah, he's correctly guessing \Nthe direction of my attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:25.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぐ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:25.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}For a human, his ears are sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:30.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぁ…　俺ぁ　「クモ」の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:30.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And his aura keeps growing, so my feathers aren't doing any damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:37.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}腕相撲　何番目に強えぇかなぁ？ ７８番ってとこじゃねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:37.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The bat uses ultrasonic waves to \Nanticipate the timing of my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:40.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}弱くもないけど 強くもないよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:40.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Unless I find a way to stop it, I can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:46.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でよ　一番強いのが ウボォーギンって男だったんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:46.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First comes rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:49.77,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつが鎖野郎に やられたらしくてな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:49.77,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His aura continues to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　そんな奴 知らないって言ってるだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This could pose a problem. Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:55.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ガキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:55.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is our chance. He's probably using his ultimate attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:59.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}次に許可なく喋ったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:59.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we can evade it, we've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ぶっ殺すぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can use my ultrasonic waves \Nto see it in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう一度。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wait, I'll try getting closer as quietly as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}レディ…　ゴー！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The sound's moving away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:25.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}竹を割ったような ガチンコ好きの単細胞だ。 その反面　時間にうるさくてよぉ よく遅刻が原因で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:25.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The sound's gone! Now, with no wingbeats...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺やフランクリンと ケンカになったが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I dive! That won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:33.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺は　素の殴り合いじゃ ボコられっぱなしだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:33.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your wings aren't like the owl's, \Nso I can hear you slice through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」設立前からの付き合いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now, show me your ultimate attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰よりも知ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He isn't acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:43.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつが…　ウボォーが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:43.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I guess a human can only hear so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}戦って負けるわけがねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In that case, I'll make my move... I'll slash your jugular!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:50.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}汚ねぇ罠にかけられたに 決まってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:50.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Keep my motions minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:54.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対に許さねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:54.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Wait until I draw her as near as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:58.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何人　ぶっ殺してでも捜し出す。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:58.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He was baiting me? I'm in trouble. But his punch will take a \Nfew milliseconds to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:02.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鎖野郎は 俺達に強い恨みを持っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:02.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have plenty of time to fly away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:10.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」に恨み？ 最近　雇われた？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:10.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:15.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}直接　知らなくても 噂で聞いたりしてねえか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:15.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I must get away! You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よく思い出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:21.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}心当たりがあったら隠さず喋れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:21.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You aren't the only one that can use sound... Paper... ...to locate others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:24.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}知らないね！ たとえ知っていても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:24.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前らなんかに教えるもんか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:31.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}血も涙もない連中だと 思ってたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:31.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:34.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仲間のために泣けるんだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:34.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He used that to deflect my shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だったら　その気持を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was close... Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:41.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ほんの少し… ほんの少しでいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:41.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I used my special attack and \Nstill couldn't bring it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:59.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前　調子乗り過ぎね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:59.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is this ultrasound, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ！ ゴン！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That stupid kid has a loud voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But I'm much better at attacking with sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}動くと切る。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is the true power of their combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:16.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}質問に答えるね 鎖野郎を知らないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:16.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They strike with sound and finish with brawn. What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:20.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言っただろ　お前らに 教えることなんか　一つもない！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:20.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do I cover my ears? No, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In the darkness, if I handicap my hearing, \Nmy reaction time will suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フェイタン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I know! Gyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:28.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やめろ。 何をやめるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:28.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His eyes are shining?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前が　やろうとしてることだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Or is that aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:35.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私がやること お前　分かるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:35.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He'll rely on his eyes, ignoring sound? Let's give him another...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:41.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}腕　へし折る気だろ。 初めは指ね　軽く爪　剥ぐ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:41.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Secret Noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:04.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい　やめとけ　ノブナガ。 ルールは忘れてないだろうね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:04.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Water significantly weakens the power of sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:09.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団員同士のマジギレ　ご法度だよ。 分かってるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:09.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Good, this is better...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もめたらコインだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can locate the owl through its aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}裏。 表！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}表だ　放してやれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Of course... They started off as wild animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}で　どうすんの？　この２人。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}when approaching their prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まだ鎖野郎のこと 聞き出せてないんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can fend off their attacks, \Nbut the ultrasound really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:41.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}知らねえなら 解放してやればいいさ。 どうだ？　パクノダ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:41.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I don't keep up the Gyo, they'll take me down before \NI can even find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:48.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２人とも 本当に心当たりはないわね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:48.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In terms of latent aura, \Nthe kid has a clear advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ホント？ ええ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Even after being hit all those times, \Nhe's taken no damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼らに鎖野郎の記憶はないわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But his level of capability is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}珍しく外れたな　お前の勘。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Without a strategy, he's just a moving target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:59.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おかしいね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:07:59.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They work in perfect sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:02.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まっ　パクノダが言うなら 間違いないだろうけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:02.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have to disrupt that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:16.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい　ゴン ここに来る時　何か　されたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:16.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I use Rock, I can defeat this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:21.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ううん　質問されただけだよ。 だよな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:21.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But then the bat might run \Nand warn the other Ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:27.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達に気づかれずに 調べたってことか？ 何を？　どうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:27.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To me, a starry night is as bright as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:32.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴らの様子からして パクノダって女の調査は かなり信頼されている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:32.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As long as I'm not in total darkness, I can see you without needing \Nto rely on my hearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:36.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勘以上の説得力を持った方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:36.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So if I cover my ears... I can attack at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:45.78,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}記憶？ ((あんた　どう？ 心当たりない？))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:45.78,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The kid has shrouded his entire \Nbody in aura to avoid damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:52.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}記憶を探る能力!? 対象者に触れることで!? だとすると合点が行く
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:52.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But that reduces the strength of his attacks, \Nmaking it impossible to stand against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　ヤバい 確かに　あの時点では
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}At this rate, he'll never defeat them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鎖野郎に 心当たりなんてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's over for this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　今は 連想してしまっている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Their weakness is that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう一度　調べられたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}their movements are always in sync!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:11.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鎖野郎と関係ないなら 帰していいんじゃねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:11.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:18.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　関係ないとは 言い切れない。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:18.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to avoid both being targeted at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:25.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}後ろで糸を引いている奴が いるはずだ。 もし鎖野郎が　普段 鎖を身に着けてなかったら？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:25.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When the owl is in front of me, the bat is directly behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:33.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この２人が　鎖野郎と認識してない だけかもしれないだろ？ 解放するのは 黒幕を吐かせてからのほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:33.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A giant wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:38.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そいつは鎖野郎じゃないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:38.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The real wall was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:41.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼は 単独で行動しているはずだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:41.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:54.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ノストラードファミリーを通じて 情報は　いくらでも入って来る。 一応　鎖野郎は 組に所属してるわけだからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:54.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He turned our teamwork against us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:10:02.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達の標的は　鎖野郎だけだ。 それ以外は　ほうっておけばいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:10:02.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If I only have one opponent, \NI can concentrate on attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:05.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だそうだ…　よかったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:05.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Once he pulls off one plan, \Nthings will go his way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:08.26,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ベェ！ いや　ダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:08.26,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But that attack won't be enough \Nto get him anywhere here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:13.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そいつは帰さねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:13.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:19.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}坊ず　「クモ」に入れよ。 俺と組もうぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:19.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First comes rock... Rock... Paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:22.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やだ！　お前らの 仲間になるくらいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:22.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死んだほうがマシだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:30.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヒヒヒ…　随分　嫌われたなぁ。 おめぇ　強化系だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:30.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I made sure to knock you west!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だったら　何だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Go back to NGL!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱり　そうだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was incredibly strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:38.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クフフ…　アッハッハッハッ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:38.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I see... This is his real ultimate attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:41.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フフフフフフ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:41.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I take back what I said. This kid can be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:46.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よう！　団長が戻るまで こいつら　ここに置いとくぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:46.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But how do I proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}入団を推薦する！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Diego has been dethroned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:53.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本気かよ。 団長が認めるはずないね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:53.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Brainwashed soldiers are running around, \Nslaughtering entire villages and towns!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:57.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　いいけど 見張りは　あんた１人でやりなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:57.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Diego has fallen? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:00.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}逃げても　私らは知らないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:00.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But we all saw the soldiers try to kill everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:10.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}似てる？ ウボォーとあの子が？ ああ 感情丸出しのとことか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:10.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Warn people in other areas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:14.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}怒ると 後先　考えなくなるとことか。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:14.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Who's interfering?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:19.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何より　そっくりなのが　他人事で 一番　力を発揮するとこか。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:19.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It was in the southeast this time. Some of my puppets have been stopped. That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:23.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつは １対１で戦うことを好んだが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:23.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Whoever they are, they're keeping \Nlow and unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:28.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一番強いのは　ノブナガと組んで 大勢と戦う時だったからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:28.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An assassin? But they are acting on their own... A decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:34.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}守るもんがあったほうが あいつにとってはいいんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:34.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is so annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}足手まといがいると 強くなるってことね。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I wanna kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:46.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}逆にノブナガの能力は タイマン専門っていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:46.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which means we cannot go. You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:50.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}限定条件つきみてぇなとこ あるからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:50.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it doesn't feel like the purpose is to bait us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:54.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ケンカのたびに　２人は組まされて ブたれてたが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:54.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're being careful not to let me catch them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:12:00.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まんざらでもなさそうだった。 はい　思い出話は そこまで！　こっから本題だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:12:00.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It may all be an act to draw you out. But perhaps I'm over-thinking things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これは ハンターサイトで入手した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:06.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ノストラードファミリー 構成員リストだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:06.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ah, how I long to indulge myself \Nin the delight of agonizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:13.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ボディーガードとして　組長の娘に ついているらしいんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:13.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It is the sweet trap of the thought process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:15.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウボォーをさらったのは こいつらだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:15.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nothing more. The answer is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:29.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鎖野郎の見た目が分からない以上 知ってる奴を見つけるしかない。 あっ　こいつ　俺が殺った 左上の奴　ペケつけといてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:29.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We can let the other Ants handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:32.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}引き続きペアで行動し
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:32.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is it our turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:35.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}リストの人物捜しに 全力を挙げてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:35.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When we were injured and on the run from the Hunters, you took us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:40.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃ　午後１０時に ここに集合ってことで！　以上。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:40.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You even gave us instruction on using our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ちょっと！ ノブナガは留守番だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It is time for us to return the favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:49.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}誰か余った奴と組みなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:49.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Someone's running around \Nand disabling my puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウフ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can you kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}痛てて。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll give you updates on their location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:06.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}甘かった… 俺が　あの場面で動いたら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:06.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:13.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヒソカは　ためらわず 俺を殺す気だった あの殺気…　動けなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:13.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can we really trust them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:17.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もし　ゴンが　あそこで 致命傷を負わされかけたら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:17.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Nah, I don't trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:23.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そしたら　俺は動けたかな？ )
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:23.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're the ones trying to earn our trust, so they'll try hard to carry out their mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:29.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((お前は　人というものを 殺せるか殺せないかでしか 判断できない))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:29.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's possible that they're looking for an \Nopportunity to stab us in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:36.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}違う ((「勝ち目のない敵とは戦うな」 俺が　口を酸っぱくして 教えたよね？))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:36.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In that case, we should treat them accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The closest village is at two o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:50.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フッ　おっかねぇなぁ。 殺す気満々って面だぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:50.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Should I skip them and head for \NTaba, forty kilometers away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}先に言っとくが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Play it safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:55.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺の間合いに入ったら斬るぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:55.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't let anyone find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.76,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.76,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's wrong? As we speak, Cheetu is racing \Ntoward East Gorteau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まともに　やり合うのは無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It seems the Hunters that replaced \Nus failed to capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:41.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何とか逃げる方法を考えよう 窓は　なし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:41.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is he headed toward us? No, if he continues on his current \Ncourse, he'll pass far to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}出口は１つ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:43.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:47.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうやって　あいつを 出口から遠ざけるか…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:47.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't try to stop me... I'm already in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:54.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}レオリオのほうは 大丈夫かなぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:54.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Hunter Association has captured three \Nhundred and nineteen Chimera Ants
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:57.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うまくゼパイルさんと 合流できてるといいけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:57.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}outside of NGL as of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:15:01.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん…。 キルア　大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:15:01.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But Colt confirmed that none of \Nthem were Squadron Leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}According to him, there are eight Squadron Leaders left \Nthat would be considered aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:11.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ねぇ　ゼパイルさんに 教えてもらったのって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:11.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hunters have encountered four, \Nbut they all got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:16.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ヤキヅケ」と「ヒラキ」と… あと何だっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:16.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Cheetu is coming to East Gorteau for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:17.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}忘れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:17.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He must know the King is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:24.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ヨコヅケ」だったっけな？ 何か違う気がするなぁ。 ゴン。 ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:24.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's choosing to return to the King's \Nservice in order to increase his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:29.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺が囮になる。 その隙に　お前だけでも逃げろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:29.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My ability is still in effect, \Nand I have more raw strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:35.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何言ってんだ！ まったくだ　やめとけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:35.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But if we let him slip away and \Nhe gains even more power, there's no telling who will win next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:44.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵の力量が分からねえほど 未熟でもあるめぇ。 隙なんか　つくらねえよ。 分かってるよ！　そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:44.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we allow more Ants like him to join the King, we'll never be able to draw the Royal Guard away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}出口が１つしかない 見通しのいい部屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you still gonna try to stop me? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こちらの言動は筒抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you are, I'll fight you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:54.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一分の隙も見せずに 俺達を監視する敵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:54.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First, we contact Morel-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:16:04.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく居合の達人であろう 奴の初太刀における間合いは 俺の倍以上は　ある そこに踏み込めば 致命傷は確実
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:16:04.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If worse comes to worst, \Nhe'll need to replace us. I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:09.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だからこそ意味があるんだ！ )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:09.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This should increase the odds \Nof capturing that Ant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:15.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やってみなきゃ分かんねえだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:15.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's Knuckle... Something's come up. Yes, I'd guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:20.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア　何　考えてんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:20.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Probably. Yes. So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:23.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつの初太刀は 俺が死んでも止めるから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:23.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その間に逃げろっつってんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はぁ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I told you to send Riakke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:34.27,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何しやがんだ　てめぇ！ 勝手なこと言うな！ あぁ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:34.27,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He'd have been perfect for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.82,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死ぬとか 簡単に言うなって言ってんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.82,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh?! I don't give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:43.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}んだと！　おめぇだって さっき言ってただろうが！ 俺は　いいんだ！ でもキルアはダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:43.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's wrong? The Chimera Ant we were tracking escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:47.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はぁ？ ハハハ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:47.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The review board didn't send \Nthe Hunter we requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:51.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}強化系にゃ 理屈が通用しねえんだよなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:51.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Who did they send? Some Hunter I've never heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:54.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死ぬ気でやらなきゃ　こっから 逃げられっこねえんだよ　バカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:54.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Probably an Association dog. An Association dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:58.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ひとの気も知らないで　勝手なこと 言ってんのは　どっちだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:58.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You mean Hunters who only take jobs \Nthrough the Hunter Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:03.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ　知んないね！　バカだもん！ ガッハハ　ハハハ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:03.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It isn't surprising that they have less talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やっぱり おめぇら　おもしれぇわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn! I should have gone \Nto talk to Riakke myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:09.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぁ　悪いようには　しねえ おとなしくしとけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:09.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't be foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:15.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前が本気なのは　よく分かってる 無駄死にするな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:15.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you do anything without board approval, the Chairman will get all the grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:22.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長が戻るまでの辛抱だ。 そこで団長のお眼鏡に かなわなきゃ帰してやるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:22.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He had to argue with the executive \Ncommittee just to get the two of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:25.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが ここで逃がすくらいなら斬る。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:25.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But they don't understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:30.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺に刀を抜かせるな。 俺が抜けば　お前らは死ぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:30.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They base it on past accomplishments \Nand donations to the Association...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:34.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ…。 あっ　思い出した！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:34.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The review board has always been inflexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:39.29,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「ヨコヌキ」だよ　「ヨコヌキ」！ 「ヤキヅケ」と「ヒラキ」と
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:39.29,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How can you be so relaxed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう一つが「ヨコヌキ」！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we underestimate the Squadron \NLeaders, we'll pay dearly for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:45.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ。 思い出した？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:45.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ　思い出した　思い出した！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}After all, they listen to their deepest desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:53.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ね！　こんな簡単なことに 気づかなかったなんて！ あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:53.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So they have the talent to quickly master
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:18:01.83,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}スッキリしたところで…。 行くか！ 本気か？　死ぬだけだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:18:01.83,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}the abilities they need the most. If we let the review board bring self-preservation \Nand formality in, we won't get help in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:07.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こちとら 居合斬りを手加減するほど 器用でも　お人よしでもねえぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:07.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Maybe that's their goal... You refer to the rumors that \Nthe Vice-Chairman's faction
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バカが！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}controls the review board?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:21.81,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}出口が　ふさがれてるなら… 別の所から出ればいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:21.81,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}who agree to vote for him in the next election?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:25.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}壁を…　チッ　どっちを追う？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:25.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's no evidence of anything \Nlike that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここは５階
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You think they're stupid enough to get caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:30.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ツリ目のほうは すぐ隣が　もう階段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:30.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Look at the facts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}黒髪のほうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They've let every Squadron Leader \Nthey've faced escape alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これで　こっちから追い込めば 袋のネズミだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If this expedition fails, \Nthe Chairman will shoulder the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:44.30,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴らは壁をぶち抜いて 逃げられるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:44.30,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're willing to do whatever it \Ntakes to guarantee that result.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:50.22,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ツリ目は下に… やはり黒髪を追うしかねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:50.22,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}As the Chimera Ants claim more victims, the voices calling for the Chairman's \Nresignation grow louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:58.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どこだ？　壁は壊れてねえし 入り口のドアも…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:58.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Too bad the voices belong to a bunch \Nof people sitting at their desks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:03.80,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア！　いるか？ ああ！　いるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:03.80,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we take out the King and five million \Npeople are already dead, we've failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:07.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうか！　最後の壁破りは囮！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:07.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We already knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:09.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}壁だけ壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:09.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The Chairman is prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:13.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}手前の部屋に隠れて 俺を　やり過ごし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:13.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When he developed this plan, he was \Nwell aware of the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:18.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}廊下に出た ２人で　あいつ　ぶっ倒すぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:18.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He knew how long assuring victory would take, and the resulting casualties...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:26.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}気配が消えた…　「絶」か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:26.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Five million is the low end... That's too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:33.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「纏」と「練」の高等応用技…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:33.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Marcos-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「円」！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The phones have been ringing nonstop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:40.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}通常は体の周囲 数ｍｍから数ｃｍの間隔で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:40.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Rumors of a coup d'état are flying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:46.31,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まとっているオーラを 自分の必要な間隔まで広げる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:46.31,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And it's been discovered that mass murders \Nare taking place all over the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:49.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この「円」の中に潜む 刺客は　おろか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:49.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is no rumor. It's actually happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:52.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}舞い落ちる木の葉の数さえ 把握できる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:52.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's going on here? Are you responsible for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:59.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いかに　お前らが気配を絶ち 音を消して近づこうと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:59.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We haven't done anything! The citizens have learned the \Ntruth about the selection?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この中に入り込めば　即座に斬る
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll discuss this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.75,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いつでも来い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.75,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Return to the office before anyone suspects you. Morel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:12.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}バカ！ チェっ　あいつ ぶっ飛ばしたかったのに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:12.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Our beloved leader, Diego, has an \Nurgent announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:21.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対無理だって 返り討ちに遭って　あの世行き。 １００％？ 「念」の基礎しか知らない俺達の かなう相手じゃないね。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:21.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}To ensure that our great leader's message \Nwill be heard throughout the nation, we request that relay speakers in all \Nregions be turned to maximum volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:27.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ヘヘっ。 何だよ？ やっとキルアらしくなったじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:27.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All televisions and radios should be on, \Nand the volume raised to maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:32.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}むちゃを言うのは俺の役。 キルアは　それを クールに止めてくれなくちゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:32.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Good evening, my beloved comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:37.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フン…。 頼りにしてるんだから！ 勝手な奴！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:37.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am Diego. I have just declared that East \NGorteau is under martial law.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:44.79,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}で　どうする？　これから。 そりゃあ　何がしたいかによるさ。 俺　あいつら　ぶっ倒したい！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:44.79,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This precaution is being taken to combat \Nmalcontents that would foment rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:48.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　そりゃ最初の趣旨から 外れちゃいないけどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:48.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I ask all comrades to stay indoors, \Nwith your doors locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:53.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}けど　そのためには 念能力の向上が必須だぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:53.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Anyone outdoors without permission will \Nbe identified as a rebel and punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:58.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴らと対等に 渡り合えるだけの潜在能力が 「念」には　あるはずなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:58.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I ask that you not lend an ear \Nto false rumors being spread, but that you follow my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:11.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを知るにはクラピカに聞くのが 一番　手っ取り早いんだけどな。 えっ　何で？ あいつらの仲間を倒したっていう 鎖野郎が　クラピカだからさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:11.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The soldiers of my special forces \Nwill be visiting your residences, to see if any rebels are hiding inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}え？ やっぱり気づいてなかったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do not open your doors for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:17.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本当なの？　それ。 十中八九な。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:17.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Their response was too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:21.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もし　そうなら 俺達にもチャンスは　ある。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:21.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It must be Killua and Gon. They weren't supposed to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:25.23,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカと同じ時期に 「念」を覚えたんだからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:25.23,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But this must be part of the Chimera Ants' plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:29.32,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達の資質に合った 俺達だけの能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:29.32,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They were so well-prepared, \NI can't believe otherwise. The citizens learning the truth about \Nthe selection wasn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:34.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも　それ以上に「旅団」と 同等以上に戦える能力が必要だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:34.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In fact, if they did, the military \Nwould have an excuse to mobilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:47.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その答えのカギを握ってるのが クラピカってことか。 ああ。 その頃 ヨークシンの中心部では
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:47.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}East Gorteau has been placed under martial law, completely isolated from the rest of the world.
